<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
    <title>Reçu {{ transaction.id }} - EFA SMART FINANCE</title>
    <style>
        @page { 
            margin: 1.5cm;
            @bottom-center {
                content: "Page " counter(page) " sur " counter(pages);
                font-size: 10px;
                color: #666;
            }
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #1a202c;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        /* Main Tables */
        .main-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .header-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #008040;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .info-table {
            width: 100%;
            background: #f7fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .info-table td {
            padding: 20px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        
        .info-table .separator {
            width: 1px;
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        /* Header */
        h1 {
            color: #008040;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .company-info {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #4a5568;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        
        .company-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #008040;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .invoice-info {
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        /* Info Labels & Values */
        .info-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #718096;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #2d3748;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        /* Status Badge */
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .status-completed {
            background-color: #d1fae5;
            color: #065f46;
            border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
        }
        
        .status-pending {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            color: #92400e;
            border: 1px solid #fde68a;
        }
        
        .status-failed {
            background-color: #fee2e2;
            color: #991b1b;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
        }
        
        /* Invoice Table */
        .invoice-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 25px 0;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .invoice-table thead {
            background-color: #008040;
        }
        
        .invoice-table th {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            text-align: left;
            color: white;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            border: none;
        }
        
        .invoice-table td {
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #4a5568;
        }
        
        .invoice-table tbody tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .text-right {
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .description {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #2d3748;
        }
        
        .sub-description {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #718096;
            margin-top: 4px;
            display: block;
        }
        
        /* Total Section */
        .total-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .total-table {
            width: 300px;
            margin-left: auto;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        
        .total-table td {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .total-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4a5568;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .total-amount {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2d3748;
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        .grand-total {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #008040;
            border-top: 2px solid #008040;
            padding-top: 10px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #718096;
            text-align: center;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .footer-content {
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .thank-you {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #008040;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        /* Watermark */
        .watermark {
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-45deg);
            font-size: 80px;
            color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05);
            font-weight: bold;
            z-index: -1;
            pointer-events: none;
            user-select: none;
        }
        
        /* Notes Section */
        .notes {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #fefce8;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #92400e;
            border-radius: 4px;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .notes-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #d97706;
        }
        
        /* Logo */
        .logo-cell {
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        
        .logo {
            max-width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Watermark -->
    <div class="watermark">EFA SMART FINANCE</div>
    
    <!-- Header Table -->
    <table class="header-table">
        <tr>
            <td width="60%" class="logo-cell">
                <div class="company-info">
                    <div class="company-name">
                       <img src="{{ app.request.schemeAndHttpHost ~ asset('images/logovert.png') }}" alt="Logo EFA SMART FINANCE" class="logo">
                    </div>
                    <div>Plateforme de Tontines Digitales</div>
                    <div>contact@efasmartfinance.com</div>
                    <div>+229 69 69 69 69</div>
                    <div>Cotonou, Bénin</div>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td width="40%" class="invoice-info">
              <h1>REÇU</h1>
                <div class="company-info">
                    <table width="100%">
                        <tr class="text-right ">
                            <td ><strong>N° TRANSACTION : </strong></td>
                            <td class="info-value">#{{ transaction.id }}</td>
                        </tr>
                        
                        <tr class="text-right ">
                            <td class="text-uppercase"><strong>DATE : </strong></td>
                            <td class="text-ight info-value">{{ transaction.createdAt|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</td>
                        </tr>
                     
                        <tr class="text-right ">
                            <td><strong>MODE : </strong></td>
                            <td class="text-rght info-value">{{ transaction.paymentMethod|upper }}</td>
                        </tr>
                        
                        <tr class="text-right ">
                            <td><strong>STATUT : </strong></td>
                            <td class="text-right info-value">
                                <span class="status-badge status-{{ transaction.statut }}">
                                    {% if transaction.statut == 'completed' %}COMPLÉTÉ
                                    {% elseif transaction.statut == 'pending' %}EN ATTENTE
                                    {% elseif transaction.statut == 'failed' %}ÉCHOUÉ
                                    {% else %}{{ transaction.statut|upper }}{% endif %}
                                </span>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <!-- Client & Tontine Info Table -->
    <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
            <td width="50%">
                <div class="info-group">
                    <div class="info-label">REÇU DE</div>
                    <div class="info-value">
                        <strong>{{ user.fullName }}</strong><br>
                        {% if user.phoneNumber %}
                            {{ user.phoneNumber }}<br>
                        {% endif %}
                        {{ user.email }}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td class="separator"></td>
            <td width="50%">
                <div class="info-group">
                    <div class="info-label">TONTINE</div>
                    <div class="info-value">
                        <strong>{{ tontine.tontineCode }}</strong><br>
                        {{ tontine.name }}<br>
                        Périodicité: {{ tontine.frequency|capitalize }}<br>
                        Montant/point: {{ tontine.amountPerPoint|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }} FCFA
                    </div>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <!-- Invoice Details Table -->
    <table class="invoice-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th width="60%">Description</th>
                <th width="40%" class="text-right">Montant</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <span class="description">
                        {% if transaction.type == 'frais_service' %}
                            Règlement des frais de service (Commissions)
                        {% else %}
                            Versement de points de tontine
                        {% endif %}
                    </span>
                    <span class="sub-description">
                        Référence tontine: {{ tontine.tontineCode }}<br>
                        Encaissement physique au guichet
                    </span>
                </td>
                <td class="text-right description">
                    {{ transaction.amount|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }} FCFA
                </td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    
    <!-- Total Section Table -->
    <div class="total-section">
        <table class="total-table">
            <tr>
                <td class="total-label grand-total">TOTAL ENCAISSÉ</td>
                <td class="total-amount grand-total">{{ transaction.amount|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }} FCFA</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Payment Notes -->
    <div class="notes">
        <div class="notes-title">NOTES</div>
        <table width="100%">
            <tr>
                <td>
                    • Ce document atteste de la réception de fonds au guichet.<br>
                    • Pour les versements de tontine, votre solde est mis à jour instantanément.<br>
                    • Pour les frais, votre tontine est désormais active pour les dépôts.<br>
                    • Conservez ce reçu comme preuve de paiement.
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
        <table width="100%" class="footer-content">
            <tr>
                <td class="text-center">
                    <div class="thank-you">MERCI POUR VOTRE FIDÉLITÉ</div>
                    <div>
                        EFA SMART FINANCE • Gestion de Tontines Digitales<br>
                        Cotonou, Bénin • contact@efasmartfinance.com<br>
                        www.efasmartfinance.com
                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
